1. Development dependencies

Quoted versions are known working versions.  Other versions might work or might
not.  Let me know about your experiences.

* bundler (~> 1.2.0)
* node.js (~> 0.8.0)
* npm (~> 1.1.0)

2. Preparing your environment

From the source tree root:

    $ git submodule update --init
    $ npm install
    $ bundle install
    $ rake js:build
    $ rake

If all examples pass, you're good to go.

3. Associated services

* https://travis-ci.org/NUBIC/jsv.rb
* https://codeclimate.com/github/NUBIC/jsv.rb
